However, objectively it has also led to the emergence of rural "hollowing" to varying degrees, especially the weakening of rural grass-roots organizations, and the village party branch secretary and party members have shown the characteristics of "one old and one low", that is, the aging of age, low academic qualifications, the leader of the village party organization is not strong, and the problem of green and yellow is not connected.
