Bringing those capable, conscious, and aspiring to serve their hometown migrant workers, guiding them to return to their hometowns to become leaders who have become rich leaders, and to train them into party members and village cadres with merit, and enrich the cadres at the grass-roots level, which is the solution to the rural party members' ranks and grass-roots party organizations.
