Zhengwan high-speed rail from Zhengzhou City, Henan Province, to the southwest through Pingdingshan City, Nanyang City, Hubei Province Xiangyang City to Chongqing Wanzhou District, the new line is about 818 kilometers long, the design speed of 350 km / h, Chongqing territory about 184 kilometers.
