"During the project construction process, we used the geological survey law, the method of material exploration and advanced drilling methods to advance the geological forecast, and adopted a special design scheme for more than 30 types of caves. For example, we have designed and built a bridge with a long length of 24 meters, spanning a large cavern in the longitudinal length of more than 10 meters and a depth of super55 meters to avoid tunnel subsidence," the Army said.
