After the completion of the full line of Zhengwan high-speed rail, it will become the new convenient and fast passenger main channel in southwest China, North China and Northeast China, which is of great significance for improving the capacity and quality of the railway channel to the northeast of the southwest region, improving the layout of the regional road network, accelerating the development of tourism resources along the route, promoting regional coordinated development, and promoting the implementation of the western development strategy.
